            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1255783</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div class="flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"><div class="min-h-[20px] text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5 overflow-x-auto" dir="auto" data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="afd15597-0a1c-4c62-b5c2-8b491895b5fe"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light"><p>2024 巴黎奥运正式完满结束，Tom Cruise 在闭幕典礼以《职业特工队》经典「吊威也」场面现身法国法兰西体育场接下奥运会旗帜，并将奥运会旗移送美国洛杉矶，象征著 2028 年奥运会将由美国洛杉矶举办。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1255787" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/cruise1200x556-694x322.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="322" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/cruise1200x556-694x322.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/cruise1200x556.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.mediaite.com/sports/watch-tom-cruise-jumps-off-roof-in-wild-mission-impossible-style-stunt-to-close-olympics/">Media ITE</a></p></div><p>Tom Cruise 在法国巴黎奥运闭幕典礼上再度展现其招牌特技，以《职业特工队》经典「吊威也」的方式由法兰西体育场顶部垂降，与场内与各国运动员互动后，接过美国洛杉矶市长 Karen Bass 及美国体操名将 Simone Biles 手中的奥运会旗。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255785" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/88107540582c11efaebc-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/88107540582c11efaebc-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/88107540582c11efaebc.jpg 800w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c3d9ervrv5mo">BBC</a></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255786" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/rs_1024x759240811144-694x514.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="514" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/rs_1024x759240811144-694x514.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/rs_1024x759240811144.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.eonline.com/news/1405958/olympics-2024-tom-cruise-ends-closing-ceremony-with-truly-impossible-stunt">eonline</a></p><p>随后现场播放早前拍摄的影片，可见 Tom Cruise 骑上电单车，在巴黎市区穿梭，然后登上飞机，最终以跳伞的方式抵达洛杉矶荷李活山，影片中可见，荷李活山的「Hollywood」字样加入了奥运五环装饰。</p></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255789" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/tomcruisehandspariso-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/tomcruisehandspariso-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/tomcruisehandspariso-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9ey4Ap4DKAM">TODAYonline</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255788" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/tomcruisehandspariso-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/tomcruisehandspariso-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/tomcruisehandspariso.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9ey4Ap4DKAM">TODAYonline</a></p><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><p>Tom Cruise 在新「Hollywood」标志前将奥运会旗交接给奥运会的山地单车运动员 Kate Courtney，象征著巴黎奥运正式落幕，而洛杉矶奥运即将揭幕。</p></div></div></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1255790" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/tomcruisehandspariso-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/tomcruisehandspariso-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/tomcruisehandspariso-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9ey4Ap4DKAM">TODAYonline</a></p><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"><div class="min-h-[20px] text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5 overflow-x-auto" dir="auto" data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="afd15597-0a1c-4c62-b5c2-8b491895b5fe"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"><div class="min-h-[20px] text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5 overflow-x-auto" dir="auto" data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="ca533d5e-a5f5-4ede-9b6f-ee26271702b0"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">Thank you, Paris! Now off to LA. <a href="https://t.co/MxlAb0hZbT">pic.twitter.com/MxlAb0hZbT</a></p><p>— Tom Cruise (@TomCruise) <a href="https://twitter.com/TomCruise/status/1822749650463732136?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">August 11, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><p>图片来源：<a href="https://consequence.net/2024/08/tom-cruise-paris-olympic-closing-ceremony/">Consequence</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://abcnews.go.com/GMA/Culture/tom-cruise-skydives-paris-olympics-closing-ceremony-epic/story?id=112763583">ABC</a>、<a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c3d9ervrv5mo">BBC</a>、<a href="https://www.eonline.com/news/1405958/olympics-2024-tom-cruise-ends-closing-ceremony-with-truly-impossible-stunt">E Online</a>、<a href="https://www.mediaite.com/sports/watch-tom-cruise-jumps-off-roof-in-wild-mission-impossible-style-stunt-to-close-olympics/">Media ite</a>、<a href="https://people.com/tom-cruise-performs-stunt-2024-paris-olympics-closing-ceremony-8693680">People</a>、<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1765804-20240812.htm">RTHK</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/05/noah-lyles/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">奥运男飞人「龟波气功」庆祝，曾开跑前哂《游戏王》卡、被日媒称「最快的宅」</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/05/olympics/life-tech/sport-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">巴黎奥运「中国制」无处不在，阿里云提供直播技术 + 主导官方纪念品市场</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/cheungkalong-ig-spam-by-italian/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">张家朗 IG 被意大利人洗版闹偷金牌　意大利剑击联盟为赛果提抗议</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/12/tom-cruise-paris-olympics-closing-ceremony-mission-impossible/movie-2/">Tom Cruise 特工式空降巴黎奥运闭幕　洛杉矶跳伞传奥运会旗</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
